Code Style and Consistency

---
description: Code Style and Consistency
globs:
  - "src/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Follow the Google Python Style Guide.
- Use type hints in every function; enforce them with mypy.
- Run Black, isort, and flake8 (or pylint) via pre-commit hooks to maintain a consistent style.
